{"tid":1662283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：中国政府無要求NBA解僱莫雷","createTime":"2019-10-18T16:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T01:36:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dca892946632b7fab43de5e4f1ec69c96269479e","tid":1662283,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:00:42.000Z","msg":"美國NBA火箭總經理莫雷（Daryl Morey）早前在社交網站貼圖撐港，NBA總裁施華周四（10月17日）表明，拒絕應中國要求開除莫雷，甚至沒有對他懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，中國外交部發言人耿爽被問到中國政府是否要求解僱莫雷，他指為此專門向有關部門作了了解和核實，結果是中國政府從來沒有提出過這樣的要求。<br />\n<br />\n莫雷早前於社交網站分享圖片，內容為「Fight For Freedom, Stand With Hong Kong」（為自由而戰，與香港站在一起），但之後刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/article/10-18-2019/56860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-18-2019%2F56860&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9oc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=af05114b\" target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/article/10-18-2019/56860</a>"},{"pid":"0d20216a7a85e420af6ca542c73e5da91b251162","tid":1662283,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:02:31.000Z","msg":"阿銀公開對話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6c26460045df4de5b2c5bfdc7beff32634598b","tid":1662283,"uid":40267,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:04:26.000Z","msg":"恥爽: 點解同一招對國泰work但nba唔work架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f9d31a2b3b1a2cf4b00172ff612ec25b7ddd53","tid":1662283,"uid":184827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc6c26460045df4de5b2c5bfdc7beff32634598b","tid":1662283,"uid":40267,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:04:26.000Z","msg":"恥爽: 點解同一招對國泰work但nba唔work架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"誰大誰惡誰正確<br />\n<br />\n你估美國流？"},{"pid":"17020408072aefe2b0e0a654583d82cb32e2a4f4","tid":1662283,"uid":176839,"like":1,"di